      "content": "but i already have some antiseptic wash and some strong antibiotic cream here at home. honestly i've had cuts like this before and they always heal fine once i just clean them up and keep them covered. if i just do a few warm soaks and apply the cream twice a day, how long should i wait before it looks better? i really need to know if this is something i can just manage myself for a few days so i don't have to waste time at the doctor.",
